  1 (0 school-type school 0)
    2 (You really enjoyed 2 school\. You hope I had a good time there\.) (100 :out)
  1 (0 school-type 0)
    2 (You really enjoyed 2 \. You hope I had a good time there\.) (100 :out)
  1 (0 degree-type degree 0)
